{"tid":760771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經合組織：特朗普政策致美國資金大幅回流　05年來首次","createTime":"2018-07-30T00:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T03:59:06.000Z","uid":141151,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"60050332a5353c21884583f211c828648b13e090","tid":760771,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:02:26.000Z","msg":"經合組織：特朗普政策致美國資金大幅回流　05年來首次<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/255648/%e7%b6%93%e5%90%88%e7%b5%84%e7%b9%94%ef%bc%9a%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96%e8%87%b4%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e8%b3%87%e9%87%91%e5%a4%a7%e5%b9%85%e5%9b%9e%e6%b5%81%e3%80%8005%e5%b9%b4%e4%be%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F255648%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e5%2590%2588%25e7%25b5%2584%25e7%25b9%2594%25ef%25bc%259a%25e7%2589%25b9%25e6%259c%2597%25e6%2599%25ae%25e6%2594%25bf%25e7%25ad%2596%25e8%2587%25b4%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e8%25b3%2587%25e9%2587%2591%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25b9%2585%25e5%259b%259e%25e6%25b5%2581%25e3%2580%258005%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e4%25be%2586%2F&d=JOglu5YfauMX5Jo8bnbi2nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=93673cf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/255648/%e7%b6%93%e5%90%88%e7%b5%84%e7%b9%94%ef%bc%9a%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96%e8%87%b4%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e8%b3%87%e9%87%91%e5%a4%a7%e5%b9%85%e5%9b%9e%e6%b5%81%e3%80%8005%e5%b9%b4%e4%be%86/</a><br />\n<br />\n經濟合作暨發展組織（OECD）一項研究表示，美國總統特朗普的減稅及就業法案，讓今年第一季度回流美國的資金，比美國向外輸出的資金為多。數據顯示，今年第一季度美國向外投資流出量為1360億美元，與上一季的2420億美元相比，下降了44%，是自2005年第四季度以來首次出現負增長，相信因為美國企業對境外投資轉趨保守，故此將外國子公司套回利潤。 隨著美國對外投資流出量下降，日本成為本季度全球最大的對外投資者。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟合作暨發展組織統計學家Maria Borga向路透社表示，美國通常是世上最大的對外投資者，若美國企業減少境外投資，會對全球資金流動造成重大影響。但她認為，這些回流資金大多是金融資產或是現金，應該不會對這些企業的海外業務的就業或增值產生直接影響。 Borga又指，特朗普的政策對全球金融的長遠影響難以估計。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國企業最近似乎有撤出中國的趨勢。有70%產品於中國生產的玩具界領頭企業孩之寶日前宣布，由於貿易戰關係，將生產線撤離中國；電子消費品企業漢威聯合國際（Honeywell International）亦聲稱會更積極尋找中國以外的供應商。</span>"},{"pid":"07c4ce97ae8b3e2ad5e52d5d2c3f4d5c3865183e","tid":760771,"uid":121146,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:07:55.000Z","msg":"讓今年第一季度回流美國的資金，比美國向外輸出的資金為多<br />\n侵帝真係好撚勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca828457ab6b9d80926b2127f0eb665596dec7b9","tid":760771,"uid":141151,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n遠離贏国<br />\n資金平安"},{"pid":"6fddef55f94ddd06ce535eaee93fba7b24c08519","tid":760771,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b8418291d7c94b76ba2c96f3388ec948b1f701","tid":760771,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07c4ce97ae8b3e2ad5e52d5d2c3f4d5c3865183e","tid":760771,"uid":121146,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:07:55.000Z","msg":"讓今年第一季度回流美國的資金，比美國向外輸出的資金為多<br />\n侵帝真係好撚勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8b517b2c81c89f9a11b218c5b467da3de52af4","tid":760771,"uid":128014,"like":2,"dislike":42,"score":-40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:20:41.000Z","msg":"其實係奧巴馬打下嘅基礎（好似係）"},{"pid":"8f449db29a6bf283a14cfeeb02dcf5b6010071ae","tid":760771,"uid":63669,"like":5,"dislike":41,"score":-36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:21:02.000Z","msg":"唔明child登仔有乜咁開心 , 你話有美國綠卡就爽姐但事實上大多數child登仔都無美國綠卡"},{"pid":"958fde3bda69d5638c84df707f3c865d550d91c6","tid":760771,"uid":112583,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"db8b517b2c81c89f9a11b218c5b467da3de52af4","tid":760771,"uid":128014,"like":2,"dislike":42,"score":-40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:20:41.000Z","msg":"其實係奧巴馬打下嘅基礎（好似係）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T0